  "system": {
    "description": "<p>You know all human languages. In addition, you may now speak with, and use your Anomaly powers on, plants and animals. Unless you specify otherwise, people you speak with will perceive you as speaking in their most comfortable language.</p><p>You may also speak with Major and Minor Anomalies, although your Anomaly powers may be ineffective depending on the Anomalies’ Domains or Foci.</p><p>Your abilities cross even the metaphysical boundaries of meaning into the realm of understanding. You may use <strong>Tip of the Tongue</strong> or <strong>As The Kids Say</strong> on anyone you’ve met, anywhere, even across the boundaries of distance and death.</p>",
